title: CI build script doesn't look for the right msbuild.log
body:
Every CI build includes this (benign) string:

```
FINDSTR: Cannot open d:\j\workspace\Microsoft_msbuild\_Windows_NT_prtest\msbuild.log
```

That's misleading and we should fix it. I probably didn't update the search-the-log part of the script when I switched to disambiguated log files.
